readme: # font-awesome-snippet-double-quotes Font Awesome snippet for atom with double quoted markup. ## Installation * In Atom, open *Settings* (*Preferences* on Mac) * Go to *Install* section * Search for `font-awesome-snippet-double-quotes` package. Once found, click `Install` button. * Done! Or, alteratively: [![apm install font-awesome-snippet-double-quotes](https://apm-badges.herokuapp.com/apm/font-awesome-snippet-double-quotes.svg)](https://atom.io/packages/font-awesome-snippet-double-quotes) ## Usage Simply type a font awesome icon name and hit tab to generate full markup, e.g. typing: fa-envelope Then pressing tab generates: ## Snippet Update Script ```bash $ ruby snippet_generator.rb ``` ## Types * .text.html
